  "title": "Audit/ Senior Audit Associate",
  "description": "<h3>Main Duties & Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Perform statutory audit procedures for clients across various sectors, ensuring accuracy, compliance, and timely completion</p></li><li><p>Prepare and draft financial statements in accordance with Singapore FRS, with exposure to accounting and corporate tax matters</p></li><li><p>Lead and manage audit engagements, including planning, execution, and reporting phases</p></li><li><p>Identify audit issues, propose practical recommendations, and assist in resolving client queries</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper documentation and ensure all working papers meet professional standards</p></li></ul><h3>Candidate Profile</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Accountancy, or currently pursuing / completed ACCA</p></li><li><p>2–3 years of relevant external audit experience</p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of Singapore FRS and audit methodology</p></li><li><p>Proactive, committed, detail-oriented, and able to work independently</p></li><li><p>A positive team player with strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li></ul><h3>Others</h3><ul><li><p>Location: Central</p></li><li><p>5-day work week</p></li><li><p>Salary: $3,000 – $$3800</p></li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please send your updated CV to<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">candy.lim@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>All applications will be treated in strict confidence.</p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd<br />DID: 6950 9738<br /><a href=\"http://www.peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://www.peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>Lim Yi Tian, Candy<br />EA License No. 02C4944<br />Registration No. R1109829</p>",
